%F A279019 a(n) = n^2 - 9*n + 20 = (n-4)*(n-5).
%F A279019 G.f.: -2*x^6/(x-1)^3. - _R. J. Mathar_, Dec 05 2016
%F A279019 a(n) = 3*a(n-1) - 3*a(n-2) + a(n-3) for n>6. - _Colin Barker_, Dec 05 2016
